column1:

性格は乱暴で残酷。
column2:
Following our experimentation with the tiger, we successfully
transformed an orc into a succubus. She exhibits extreme hostility toward humans, and she has a violent and cruel personality.

column1:

あっという間に吸い尽くされ骨と皮だけになってしまった。
一切容赦のない、魔物が人間を襲う行為そのものだった。
column2:
One researcher succumbed to her temptation, and foolishly had sex with her.
Almost instantly, he was entirely absorbed, leaving only skin and bone.
This reflects the way a monster will attack a human without mercy.

column1:

結果2名もの死者を出すこととなった。
元がオークだからと言って、決して甘く見てはいけない。
column2:
Another researcher entered to assist the first. He too was
overpowered and raped, resulting in two deaths that day.
She must not be taken lightly simply because she was originally an orc.

column1:
また、オークのオスは彼女に対して物凄く発情するようだ。
2~3匹オークのオスを搾り殺すと大人しくなる為、
暴れ始めた場合はオークを与えること。
column2:
Also, male orcs grow extremely aroused when nearby her.
She grows docile after draining 2-3 orcs. If she is growing too
angry, leave her alone with some male orcs.

column1:

今のところ彼女が子供を産む気配はない。
column2:
Lastly, while normal orcs are incredibly fertile, there has been
no indication that she will have any children.
